item.title: Hello world!
item.dc:creator: root
item.content:encoded: Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!

wp:comment.wp:comment_content: Hi, this is a comment. To get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in the dashboard. Commenter avatars come from Gravatar.

item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: root
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Ribbon Earrings
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded:
Evocative of the slender thread one might tie around one’s finger to remember something—or someone—Tiffany Bow is a charming symbol of our most important ties. Traced in diamonds, this design captures the sweeping movement of a flowing ribbon.
  • 18k rose gold with round brilliant diamonds
  • Size mini
  • Carat total weight .34

item.title: Ribbon Ring
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded:
Evocative of the slender thread one might tie around one’s finger to remember something—or someone—Tiffany Bow is a charming symbol of our most important ties. Sparkling diamonds add an element of glamour to this feminine design.
  • 18k rose gold with round brilliant diamonds
  • Carat total weight .20

item.title: Cuff

Evocative of the slender thread one might tie around one’s finger to remember something—or someone—Tiffany Bow is a charming symbol of our most important ties. Traced in diamonds, this design captures the sweeping movement of a flowing ribbon.
  • 18k rose gold with round brilliant diamonds
  • Medium, fits wrists up to 6.25"
  • Carat total weight .82

item.title: Double Interlocking Drop Pendant
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded:
Proudly inscribed with the year Tiffany was founded, the Tiffany 1837™ collection is defined by sleek curves and contours. This pendant's interlocking design is a dynamic finishing touch to any look.
  • Sterling silver and Rubedo™ metal
  • Size small
  • Adjustable, 16-18" long
  • Developed in honor of Tiffany’s 175th anniversary, Rubedo™ metal glows with a delicate, rosy luminescence inspired by the light of dawn

item.title: Alternating Ring
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded:
Inspired by the fire and radiance of our superlative diamonds, Tiffany Victoria uses a unique combination of cuts for a distinctly romantic sensibility. The feminine arrangement of this ring is the embodiment of subtle glamour.
  • Platinum with diamonds
  • Marquise diamonds, carat total weight .79
  • Round brilliant diamonds, carat total weight 1.14

item.title: ANGELIC SQUARE NECKLACE
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded: Brighten up your jewelry box with this stunning rhodium-plated necklace with a sensual color injection. Showcasing square crystals in shades of blue, framed with classic crystal pavé, this is an easy-to-wear piece that will still feel timeless in years to come. Perfect for gifting or an elegant choice for a wedding.

item.title: Diamonds by the Yard Earrings
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded:
Tiffany round diamonds catch the light and make it dance. Earrings in platinum with pear-shaped and round brilliant diamonds. Pear-shaped diamonds, carat total weight .50; round brilliant diamonds, carat total weight .16. Original designs copyrighted by Elsa Peretti.
  • Pear-shaped diamonds, carat total weight .50
  • round brilliant diamonds, carat total weight .16.

item.title: CRYSTALDUST CUFF
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded: Crafted using our Crystal Rock technique, the irresistible Crystaldust Cuff is a new signature Swarovski design to equal Stardust and Slake. It is lavishly encrusted with chrome-effect crystals for unparalleled sparkle. Its open-shank silhouette is on-trend and comfortable, whilst the stainless steel capped ends, embellished with crystals, finish its clean design perfectly. Wear alone as a perfect finishing touch or layer with others for maximum impact.

item.title: Wedding Band Ring
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded: An original creation of incomparable beauty. Band ring with a diamond in platinum. 4mm wide.

item.title: Olive Leaf Pendant
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded: Inspired by the olive branch, a symbol of peace and abundance. Pendant in 18k rose gold. Size small, on an 18" chain. Original designs copyrighted by Paloma Picasso.

item.title: Paloma's sugar stacks
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded: Luscious colours, designed to be stacked or worn alone. In 18k gold with a blue topaz. Carat weight 1.00. Original designs copyrighted by Paloma Picasso.

item.title: Wire Hoop Earrings
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded: Graphic angles and clean lines blend to create the beautiful clarity of the Tiffany T collection. These elegant hoops are a modern interpretation of a classic design.

item.title: Love Bracelet
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded: Featuring Paloma Picasso’s own handwriting, this expressive collection was inspired by graffiti scrawled on New York buildings. This bracelet's heartfelt sentiment creates a timeless design.

item.title: Crystalline Hours Watch
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded: Make a bold fashion statement with this unique and eye-catching timepiece for women, which upgrades a casual outfit or complements a luxurious evening look. Created in collaboration with renowned watch designer Eric Giroud, the retro-inspired design features a dial filled with 2’000 rose gold-tone crystals for the ultimate Swarovski signature sparkle. A rose gold-tone coated stainless steel case and white genuine leather strap complete the design. Specifications: Case - 38 mm; Water resistant up to 50 m; Swiss made.

item.title: Ginger Necklace
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded: Add dark sparkle to any outfit with this necklace with an on-trend pear silhouette. An ideal gift, the easy-to-wear design elegantly combines rose gold plating and gray crystal pavé. Layer with other styles for a fashion-forward look.

item.title: Dreamy Watch
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded: Timeless elegance with a touch of modernity, this sophisticated timepiece can be worn day or night. It features a black leather strap, a stainless steel case, and a black sunray dial with 11 hand-applied crystal markers. Case - 28 mm; Water resistant up to 30 m; Swiss made. Treat yourself or someone special to this stylish watch.

item.title: Solitaire Diamond Earrings
item.dc:creator: root
item.excerpt:encoded: Meticulously matched for size, color, clarity and presence. Earrings of round brilliant diamonds in 18k rose gold, for pierced ears. Round brilliant diamonds, carat total weight .22.
